what_worked: Applied early_filter, pushdown, date_cte_isolate: Created early-filtering CTEs for item, date_dim, and inventory to reduce data before the final join, and converted catalog_sales join to an EXISTS subquery to avoid unnecessary data multiplication.
why_it_worked: Applying selective filters early reduces intermediate row counts before expensive operations; Pushing predicates closer to table scans reduces data volume in upper operators; Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows
